negative.review: I thought it would be an improved version of ROTK 13, but boy was I wrong. The game is made too easy, there's not much immersion compared 13. They tried to make the battling system "better" but I'm not a big fan of the grids. It's another quick cash grab by KOEI for ROTK fans. Stick to the 13th game, the best one imo.
Editor DLC for Specaility Items does not work.
